{"tid":1980416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：市道不景氣令反共派選擇公務員鐵飯碗 倡入職時增宣誓效忠環節","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T07:33:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"805b9a4e79f841c5ab6ad3b520cb71554493107f","tid":1980416,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"公務員入職加宣誓環節 當局冀今屆立法會會期內交報告<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長羅智光表示，公務員需要加強對《基本法》的認識和培訓，<span style=\"color: gold;\">期望今屆會期暑假結束前，能夠就公務員入職時加設宣誓環節的事宜，向立法會提交報告。</span><br />\n<br />\n羅智光出席立法會一個委員會時又說，各項延長公務員服務年期的措施自2015年推行後，至少大致運作暢順，公務員對延遲退休方案反應正面，選擇延遲退休的人數一直穩步上升，截至今年2月16日總共有大約27400名公務員選擇延遲退休，佔整體合資格公務員的49%，當中大約17200人是文職人員，10200人是紀律部隊人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521578-20200420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521578-20200420.htm&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=2da4f9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521578-20200420.htm&h=83c7dc36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521578-20200420.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n羅智光相信今年申請入職公務員人數會比往年多<br />\n20.04.2020 13:14<br />\n<br />\n在立法會一個委員會上，工聯會郭偉強關注，現時仍有2成半公務員未實行5天工作制，擔心長遠會影響公務員的競爭力。公務員事務局長羅智光表示，5天工作制是大方向，又說，<span style=\"color: gold;\">今年市道不是特別好，相信申請入職公務員的人數比往年多</span>，他又指，自2015年實施延長公務員服務年期的安排後，措施大致運作順暢。<br />\n<br />\n建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界謝偉銓關注，疫情下公務員積聚大量工作，加上第二輪防疫抗疫基金提出加開公務員及青年實習的職位，擔心加重公務員的壓力，建議再增加挽留已達退休年齡的公務員。羅智光表示，各部門會按照實際運作需要挽留人手，而基金提出增聘的職位都是臨時性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282083&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282083%26csid%3D261_341&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=7007d296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282083&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6ddac0435d3d7e757c03f2d91130267d4bbb6f02","tid":1980416,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"驚呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95321a8b376407ba57896723dad83d87bf114fd4","tid":1980416,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0de34357b5bb18936b380c8610d470424e5673a","tid":1980416,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"截至今年2月16日總共有大約27400名公務員選擇延遲退休，佔整體合資格公務員的49%，當中大約17200人是文職人員，10200人是紀律部隊人員。<br />\n做到70歲啦 香港人下一代邊有好日子過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92513241516f94d99c889f9ed937dca52b8db6ed","tid":1980416,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:40:55.000Z","msg":"child 登：唔好鬥黃"},{"pid":"215119077054cc938a69f4636e2efb0ad7df91cc","tid":1980416,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"宣唔宣誓咪又係炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7473abc3cdcfa0ef378340bc1e38c4b675abe0a3","tid":1980416,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9170d085bd06bf206aeb4ccf96e9efde59f983b4","tid":1980416,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"宣誓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨白紙黑字寫明都唔認數, 宣誓有幾難"},{"pid":"77f2daf716d452460fe433a4901fb2da9aabfc87","tid":1980416,"uid":111322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"如果宣誓有用 咁勾勾手指尾都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\